    {
      "id": "PopularPost227564",
      "post_content": "Why so much hate on majinara's comment? Four mana for conditional evasion indeed sucks.  \n  \nSo yeah, this is simply some sort of [Fear](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fear) in equipment form,  \nexcept that it gets more awesome on colorless creatures and less awesome on multicolored ones.  \n  \nBut compared to [Whispersilk Cloak](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Whispersilk Cloak) or [Cloak of Mists](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Cloak of Mists) you feel like either the equip or the casting cost could have been lowered to ![1](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=1&type=symbol). (In the latter case it could have been interesting with [Trinket Mage](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Trinket Mage) or the like.)  \n  \nBut yeah we didn't get a cloak, we just got a hood.  \nAnd not a particularly intimidating one regarding playability :P",
      "posted_by": "Mode",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost227564\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">Why so much hate on majinara's comment? Four mana for conditional evasion indeed sucks.<br/><br/>So yeah, this is simply some sort of <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Fear\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fear\">Fear</a> in equipment form,<br/>except that it gets more awesome on colorless creatures and less awesome on multicolored ones.<br/><br/>But compared to <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Whispersilk Cloak\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Whispersilk Cloak\">Whispersilk Cloak</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Cloak of Mists\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Cloak of Mists\">Cloak of Mists</a> you feel like either the equip or the casting cost could have been lowered to <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"1\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=1&amp;type=symbol\"/>. (In the latter case it could have been interesting with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Trinket Mage\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Trinket Mage\">Trinket Mage</a> or the like.)<br/><br/>But yeah we didn't get a cloak, we just got a hood.<br/>And not a particularly intimidating one regarding playability :P</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '227564'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy416\">Mode</span>\r\n                                (2/11/2012 5:22:28 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>"
